      • onItemRightClick

        @Nonnull
public net.minecraft.util.ActionResult<net.minecraft.item.ItemStack> onItemRightClick(@Nonnull

                                                                                                @Nonnull

                                                                                                @Nonnull
                                                                                                net.minecraft.util.Hand hand)
        Handle the right clicking event

        On the server side, do nothing

        On the client side, if the player is Crouching, send packet to server to open GUI; otherwise, do searching according to the NBT of the compass
